item.title: CVE-2022-30628|2024-08-03T06:56:13.002Z -- supersmart.me -- supersmart.me%20%E2%80%93%20walk%20through
item.description: It was possible to download all receipts without authentication. Must first access the API https://XXXX.supersmart.me/services/v4/customer/signin to get a TOKEN. Then you can then access the API that provides invoice images based on the URL https://XXXX.supersmart.me/services/v4/invoiceImg?orderId=XXXXX
